&lt;p&gt;Chris is a dedicated software engineer with a passion for building cutting-edge solutions to unsolved problems. Chris has ten years of industry experience in diverse technologies from mobile, networking, web, to augmented reality, in such sectors from the mobile apps scene, genealogical societies, medical simulation, to big-data processing at Amazon scale. Chris currently works at Amazon in Tempe, AZ, and we&apos;re hiring.&lt;/p&gt;
